From: John Reck <jreck@google.com>
Date: Fri, 7 Nov 2025 13:41:04 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add mimetype filter to LocalImageResolver

Only allow "trusted" codecs

Test: LocalImageResolverTest
Bug: 456471290
Flag: EXEMPT BUGFIX

(cherry picked from commit e69ce2095f902a9f2ebd1871e9a0bda06908f0ab)
